    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "that makes sense. i've been reading a lot about the environmental side of it though, like how it's being framed as a key part of hitting climate goals. do most experts agree that it's pretty much a requirement for making cities sustainable? or is there actual debate about whether it even works for the environment?",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
